The evidence with the title 'Anatomy of a stump speech - interactive feature - nytimes.com ' says Jan 3, 2012  ... In the four years i was speaker , not only did we balance the budget, paid off $405 billion of debt, we balanced it for four straight years, two while i was speaker and two in the immediate following years based on the policies we established. But in addition to all that, there were 11 million new jobs created. 
